::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica and Bloodystrike cut through several bushes, coming up to the 
fallen femm. Reptilica bends down toward her, turning her over with. He steps 
back, whistling in apreciation.

"Not bad!" he says, looking over the female's curves, "Not bad at all."

By his side, Bloodystrike nods his agreement, his eyes also glued to the 
femm. "Let's get her back to base."

Reptilica nods, grabbing one arm of the femm while Bloodystrike grabs the 
other. They lift her to their shoulders, walking off toward the Alliance base.
